DataElement.preferredName: Smoking History Daily Cigarette Consumption java.lang.Integer
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A record of an individual's background in regard to smoking tobacco.  This would include such factors as start date, end date (if applicable), number of cigarette smoked, attempts to quit, and others._Occurring or done each day.:Finely cut tobacco encased in a wrapper of thin paper and rolled for smoking.:The bodily process of taking in and using up something, especially the eating or drinking of something._Generic value domain for a primitive java dataype that is an Integer (32-bit two's complement).
